sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    actor Student
    participant Frontend as Frontend (StreamLit)
    participant Backend as FastAPI Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (pgvector)
    participant AI as Ollama LLM

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note right of Student: Phase 1: Upload & Asynchronous Processing
        Student->>Frontend: Uploads PDF Material
        Frontend->>Backend: POST /materials/upload
        
        %% Async background task starts here
        Backend->>AI: Send chunks for Embeddings & Question Generation
        Note over AI: LLM processes text chunks<br/>and generates questions ahead of time
        AI-->>Backend: Return Vectors & Generated Questions (JSON)
        
        Backend->>DB: Store DocumentChunks, Vectors, and Questions
        DB-->>Backend: Confirm storage
        Backend-->>Frontend: 200 OK (Upload & Processing Complete)
    end
    
    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note right of Student: Phase 2: Quiz Generation & Execution
        Student->>Frontend: Clicks "Start Quiz"
        Frontend->>Backend: POST /quizzes/generate/ (topic_id, length)
        
        %% Fast synchronous retrieval
        Backend->>DB: SQL Query: Select [length] random/targeted questions for [topic_id]
        DB-->>Backend: Return pre-generated questions
        
        Backend-->>Frontend: Return Quiz Data payload
        Frontend-->>Student: Display the first question
    end